* [[:en:Eiroku|Eiroku]] 9th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} [[1566]] [[December 30]]) – {{ill|Mōri Motonari|ja|毛利元就|qq=|12=draft}} defeated {{ill|Amako Yoshiaki|ja|尼子義久|qq=|12=draft}} at Tomida Tsukiyama Castle, leading to the extinction of the Amako clan.
