== Events == * {{ill|Shōkyō|ja|正恭|qq=|qq=draft}} 4th year / {{ill|Kenmu|ja|建武|qq=|qq=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1336]] [[January 2]]) – {{ill|Nitta Yoshisada|ja|新田義貞|qq=|qq=draft}} and his forces departed Kyoto to pursue {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|足利尊氏|qq=|qq=draft}}. * [[:en:Eiroku|Eiroku]] 9th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1566]] [[December 30]]) – {{ill|Mōri Motonari|ja|毛利元就|qq=|qq=draft}} defeated {{ill|Amako Yoshiaki|ja|尼子義久|qq=|qq=draft}} at Tomida Tsukiyama Castle, leading to the extinction of the Amako clan. * {{ill|Kansei|ja|寛政|qq=|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1790]] [[January 4]]) – {{ill|Tanikaze Kajinosuke (2nd)|ja|谷風梶之助|qq=|qq=draft}} received permission for the first yokozuna ring-entering ceremony.
== Births == * {{ill|Genna|ja|元和|qq=|qq=draft}} 9th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1624]] [[January 9]]) – {{ill|Meisei Tennō|ja|明正天皇|qq=|qq=draft}}, the 109th Emperor of Japan (died [[1696]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=|qq=draft}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1828]] [[January 5]]) – {{ill|Kobayashi Issa|ja|小林一茶|qq=|qq=draft}}, a haiku poet (born [[1763]]).
