== Events == * {{ill|Shōkyō|ja|正恭|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōkyō|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} 4th year / [[:en:Jianwu|Kenmu]] 2nd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1336|1336]] [[:en:January 2|January 2]]) – [[:en:Nitta Yoshisada|Nitta Yoshisada]] and his forces departed Kyoto to pursue [[:en:Ashikaga Takauji|Ashikaga Takauji]]. * [[:en:Eiroku|Eiroku]] 9th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1566|1566]] [[:en:December 30|December 30]]) – [[:en:Mōri Motonari|Mōri Motonari]] defeated [[:en:Amago Yoshihisa|Amako Yoshiaki]] at Tomida Tsukiyama Castle, leading to the extinction of the Amako clan. * [[:en:Kansei|Kansei]] 1st year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1790|1790]] [[:en:January 4|January 4]]) – {{ill|Tanikaze Kajinosuke (2nd)|ja|谷風梶之助|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tanikaze Kajinosuke (2nd)|qq=}} received permission for the first yokozuna ring-entering ceremony.
== Births == * [[:en:Yuanhe|Genna]] 9th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1624|1624]] [[:en:January 9|January 9]]) – [[:en:Empress Meishō|Meisei Tennō]], the 109th Emperor of Japan (died [[:en:1696|1696]]).
