'''November 19''' is the 19th day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November (Shimotsuki)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November (Lunisolar)|qq=}} the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Taian|WD=Q96759844|1=taian}}{{efn|ja|大安|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taian|1=taian|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q1306255}}.

== Events ==
* {{ill|Shōkyō|1=Shōkyō|2=ja|3=正慶|ja|正恭|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōkyō|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q1069086}} 4th year / {{ill|Jianwu|en|Jianwu|WD=Q11065423|lt=Kenmu|1=Jianwu}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|WD=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1336|en|1336|WD=Q6028|lt=1336|1=1336}} {{ill|January 2|en|January 2|WD=Q2151|lt=January 2|1=January 2}}) – {{ill|Nitta Yoshisada|en|Nitta Yoshisada|WD=Q1328796|lt=Nitta Yoshisada|1=Nitta Yoshisada}} and his forces departed Kyoto to pursue {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|en|Ashikaga Takauji|WD=Q297107|lt=Ashikaga Takauji|1=Ashikaga Takauji}}.
* {{ill|Eiroku|en|Eiroku|WD=Q1143341|lt=Eiroku|1=Eiroku}} 9th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|WD=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1566|en|1566|WD=Q6638|lt=1566|1=1566}} {{ill|December 30|en|December 30|WD=Q2901|lt=December 30|1=December 30}}) – {{ill|Mōri Motonari|en|Mōri Motonari|WD=Q1156545|lt=Mōri Motonari|1=Mōri Motonari}} defeated {{ill|Amago Yoshihisa|en|Amago Yoshihisa|WD=Q837428|lt=Amako Yoshiaki|1=Amago Yoshihisa}} at Tomida Tsukiyama Castle, leading to the extinction of the Amako clan.
* {{ill|Kansei|en|Kansei|WD=Q1195131|lt=Kansei|1=Kansei}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1790|en|1790|WD=Q7775|lt=1790|1=1790}} {{ill|January 4|en|January 4|WD=Q2168|lt=January 4|1=January 4}}) – {{ill|Tanikaze Kajinosuke (2nd)|ja|谷風梶之助|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tanikaze Kajinosuke (2nd)|1=Q27500648|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q27500648}} received permission for the first yokozuna ring-entering ceremony.

